I get this question a lot – “What are the best foundations for all skin types & under budget?” 💁🏻‍♀️ So here are 2 must-haves you should definitely keep in your vanity if you’re a makeup artist (especially if you’re a beginner)! 💼✨

🔹 Forever52 Ultra Definition Liquid Foundation – Gives a beautiful finish and flawless base every time! @forever52india 
🔹Charmacy Milano Foundation – Works on all skin types, gives amazing coverage and a flawless look too! @charmacymilano 

💸 Both foundations are under ₹1000 and are total value for money!
So if you’re looking for the best affordable foundations, definitely consider these two. 👌

#AffordableFoundation #MakeupArtistEssentials #FoundationForAllSkinTypes #MakeupUnder1000 #Forever52Foundation #charmacymilano #FlawlessBase #BudgetFriendlyMakeup

Queen of Mattes 👑💄 – Brown Lipstick Lovers, This One’s for You!
This lip combo from @reachedmars is called Queen of Mattes and it comes with 3 stunning shades – all from the brown family (and you already know how much I LOVE brown lipsticks 😍).
I’ve swatched all 3 shades for you in this video so you can pick your fave!
If you like this combo, just comment below for the link – I’ll send it your way! 🤎✨

#marscosmetics #reachedmars #QueenOfMattes #BrownLipstickLove #LipstickSwatches #MatteLipCombo #MakeupReel #LipstickAddict

Soft Glam Look using @justgoldindia HD Cover Foundation ✨
Today I used two shades of the Just Gold HD Cover Foundation — one lighter and one darker — and mixed them to get my perfect skin tone match. This foundation gives medium to full coverage and also comes with SPF 15 protection, which is a big plus! 💁🏻‍♀️
@makeupempirein 
To blend everything seamlessly, I used Just Gold brushes — and trust me, they work so well for applying foundation and blending blush effortlessly. 😍

If you’re looking to customize your base shade, try mixing two shades like this! 💡

#JustGoldBeauty #SoftGlamLook #FoundationHack #MakeupWithNisha #BlendLikeAPro

This sunscreen is truly a @sotrue.beauty find! 💯
When I spotted it on Flipkart, I was instantly impressed by its features —
✅ No white cast
✅ Matte finish
✅ No chip-chip feel
✅ No added fragrance
And the best part? It’s suitable for all skin types! 😍
If you’ve been searching for an everyday sunscreen that checks all the right boxes, you should definitely give this one a try. 💛 #SunscreenForAll #MatteFinish #NoWhiteCast #SkincareFinds #flipkartfinds #sotrue

I just couldn’t resist sharing this one! ✨
This Purple Blue perfume from @naseemperfume @naseemperfumeindia is hands down the best perfume I’ve ever used! 💜💙

What makes it even more special? It’s completely alcohol-free and comes in a unique milky texture that feels so luxe! 😍

I loved it so much, I even ordered Shabab for my husband and Amethyst Love for my brother — because good fragrances are meant to be shared! 💕

This one’s truly a must-have in your collection!

Its perfect angular shape and soft, densely packed bristles make blending super easy — whether it’s under your eyes, around your mouth (yes, that tricky monkey mouth area 🙈), or even for contouring!

It reaches every corner effortlessly and gives that smooth, flawless finish ✨
Trust me, this is a must-have brush in your kit!

I’ve been using this mascara from @fashioncolourofficial for a while now and I’m seriously impressed! 😍
It comes with two wands — one for your upper lashes and another for your lower lashes. The lower lash wand is the thinnest I’ve ever seen, making it super easy to coat even the tiniest lashes effortlessly. 😍✨
The formula gives amazing length and volume, making your lashes pop without clumping!
If you’re a makeup artist or even just a makeup lover, this is a must-have in your kit. 💯
